These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, havana, baccarat
1. the havana-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the baccarat-smoker and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Cigar   | havana     | fonseca    | baccarat   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, potato, cabbage
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person eating cabbage is between the person eating eggplant and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Food     | potato | cabbage | eggplant         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, azalea, sunflower
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person who growsazalea and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola     | tea |
| Flower        | azalea  | sunflower | poppy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, r&b, soul
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, potato, lime
1. the fan of funk is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the fan of soul is between the person eating potato and the person eating watermelon##2
3. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | soul     | funk |
| Food           | potato | lime | watermelon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, french, egyptian
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the egyptian##1
3. the spanish is between the egyptian and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Nationality     | egyptian    | spanish | french    |

