.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, daisy
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growslily##2
2. the person who growslily is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Flower   | lily  | rose   | daisy        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, train
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person eating pineapple and the person driving the airplane##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Transport   | airplane | quad-bike | train     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, western
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, jazz, d&b
1. the person watching satire movies is the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | comedy  | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | jazz | d&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, may
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Birthday       | may | january | september  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

