.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, social-worker
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, bridge
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the lawyer is between the person playing bridge and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | social-worker | lawyer | fisherman |
| Game   | bridge     | mah-jongg    | go |

