There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is between the fan of folk and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | folk | metal      | jazz      |
| Food       | kale  | zucchini | blueberry |

